name: Godito Go
description: Godito Go. The game you have all been waiting for. Pop various heads, enjoy amazing power ups, and rack up Bucks to purchase upgrades from the store. Fight your way to the top of the leaderboards in Godito Go's three game modes, Classic, Timed, and Hardcore, all varying in difficulty. Which are you qualified for? This could be the sexiest thing to come to mankind in the history of sexy things to come to mankind, maybe ever. Buy the game, or live a lame (life). THIS. Is how mafia works.
